1. Registration

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Login as Login Page
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Home as Home Page

    User->>Login: Enter Credentials
    Login->>Auth: Validate(user, pass)
    
    Note over Auth, DB: Logic for checking credentials
    Auth->>DB: Query User Records
    DB-->>Auth: User Found / Not Found

    alt New Registration
        Auth->>DB: Create New Record
        DB-->>Auth: Success
        Auth-->>Login: Account Created
        Login->>Home: Redirect to Dashboard
    else Successful Login
        Auth-->>Login: Token Issued
        Login->>Home: Redirect to Dashboard
    else Rejected
        Auth-->>Login: 401 Unauthorized
        Login-->>User: Show Error Message
    end

2. Authentication

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as New User
    actor Admin as Admin / Moderator
    participant System as Authentication Page(only for admin)
    participant DB as Database

    User->>System: Register (Selects Role: Faculty/Student/Recruiter)
    System->>DB: Create Pending Profile
    System->>Admin: Alert: New Role Verification Required

    Note over Admin, System: Admin reviews credentials based on Role Type

    alt Approved
        Admin->>System: Confirm Verification
        System->>DB: Update Status to "Active"
        System->>DB: Assign Permissions (Faculty/Student/Recruiter)
        System-->>User: Verification Success (Access Granted)
    else Rejected
        Admin->>System: Reject Application
        System->>DB: Update Status to "Suspended"
        System-->>User: Notification: Verification Failed
    end


2. Placement Drive Application Management
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Recruiter
    actor Admin
    participant Reg as Drive Registration Page
    participant System as Admin Panel
    participant DB as Database

    Recruiter->>Reg: Register Drive (Select Dates)
    activate Reg
    Reg->>DB: Create New Drive Entry (Status: Pending)
    DB->>Admin: Alert: New Drive requested!
    deactivate Reg
    
    Note over Admin, System: Admin reviews dates on Admin Panel
    
    Admin->>System: Process Request (Approve/Reject)
    activate System
    System->>Reg: Send Decision
    deactivate System

    alt Approved
        Reg->>DB: Update Status to "Approved"
        Reg-->>Recruiter: Drive Confirmed!
    else Rejected
        Reg->>DB: Update Status to "Review Required"
        Reg-->>Recruiter: Please Reschedule (Dates Unavailable)
    end



3. Alumni Engagement & Career Support

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    actor Alumni
    participant Page as Alumni Chat Page
    participant DB as Database

    Note over User, Alumni: Real-time Discussion Flow

    User->>Page: Posts query ("How is the placement?")
    Page->>DB: Save Message
    
    par Notification Broadcast
        DB-->>User: Message sent status
        DB-->>Alumni: Alert: New query from User
    end

    Alumni->>Page: Types reply ("It's great!")
    Page->>DB: Save Message

    par Notification Broadcast
        DB-->>Alumni: Message sent status
        DB-->>User: Alert: New reply from Alumni
    end 



5. Offer Generation, Acceptance & Tracking
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Recruiter
    actor Student
    actor Admin
    participant System as Offer Page
    participant DB as Database

    Recruiter->>System: Upload Offer Details (CTC, Role, PDF)
    System->>DB: Store Offer (Status: Pending)
    System-->>Student: Notification: New Offer Received!

    Note over Student: Student reviews offer terms

    alt Offer Accepted
        Student->>System: Accept Offer
        System->>DB: Update Placement Status (Status: Placed)
        System->>Admin: Update Placement Records
        System-->>Recruiter: Share Candidate Acceptance
    else Offer Rejected
        Student->>System: Reject Offer
        System->>DB: Update Offer (Status: Declined)
        System-->>Recruiter: Share Candidate Rejection
    end


6. Career Preparation & Assessment
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Faculty
    actor Student
    participant System as Faculty Page
    participant DB as Database

    Faculty->>System: Upload Course Material / Mock Test
    System->>DB: Store Content & Key
    System-->>Student: Notification: New Prep Material Available

    Note over Student: Learning & Assessment Phase

    Student->>System: Attend Course / Submit Test Answers
    activate System
    System->>System: Auto-grade / Evaluate Performance
    System->>DB: Save Score & Progress
    deactivate System

    System-->>Student: Display Results & Personalized Feedback
    System-->>Faculty: Generate Class Performance Report

7. Faculty Engagement & Course Support
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Faculty
    actor Student
    participant CoursePage as Course Dashboard
    participant DoubtPortal as Doubt Portal
    participant DB as Database

    Faculty->>CoursePage: Upload Learning Material (PDF/Video)
    CoursePage->>DB: Save Content
    DB-->>Student: Push Notification: New Material Added

    Note over Student, CoursePage: Student studying phase

    Student->>CoursePage: View/Download Content
    Student->>DoubtPortal: Submit Specific Doubt
    DoubtPortal->>DB: Log Doubt (Status: Unresolved)
    DB-->>Faculty: Alert: New Student Query

    Faculty->>DoubtPortal: Post Response/Clarification
    DoubtPortal->>DB: Update Doubt (Status: Resolved)
    DB-->>Student: Deliver Response
